Collection for Technical Information
CrickMdoes not collect any personal data about you on its websites, apart from information which you volunteer (for example by submitting an advert, emailing the company, etc.). Any information, which you provide in this way, is not made available to any third party – other than those working with CrickMon normal business and is used by CrickMonly in line with the purpose for which you provided it.
Collection and use of technical information
